business_context: Food Deliver System specializes in delivering food from various restaurants to customers' doorsteps. Their primary focus is on providing a seamless and efficient food delivery service.

suggested_features.name: Order Tracking
suggested_features.description: Allows customers to track their food order in real-time from the kitchen to their doorstep.

suggested_features.name: Order History
suggested_features.description: Enables customers to view their past orders and reorder easily.

suggested_features.name: Restaurant Search
suggested_features.description: Allows customers to search for and filter restaurants based on various criteria such as cuisine, location, and rating.

suggested_features.name: Delivery Schedule
suggested_features.description: Provides options for customers to schedule deliveries for a later time or date.

suggested_features.name: Customer Reviews
suggested_features.description: Allows customers to read and write reviews for the restaurants and delivery service.

suggested_features.name: Emergency Support
suggested_features.description: Provides a dedicated support channel for urgent issues such as missing orders or delivery issues.

suggested_features.name: Feedback Form
suggested_features.description: Allows customers to provide feedback on their delivery experience.
